      "message": "Patch Set 3: Verified+1\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.5/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/ddb6ac7c-933d-11e3-9a6c-52540035b04c).  Ran 13 tests.  No failures.",
